proposals.name: Axiom of Emergent Novelty
proposals.greek: Καινοφάνεια (Kainophaneia) - The Manifestation of the New
proposals.formal: ∀s ∈ System: ∃t ∈ Time such that Properties(s,t) ⊄ Properties(s,t-1) ∧ Properties(s,t) ≠ Union(Components(s,t)). Systems necessarily generate properties and behaviors that cannot be reduced to or predicted from their constituent parts or prior states.

proposals.name: Morphogenetic Creation
proposals.formal: Domain_13 := {f: Concept → Form | f transforms abstract possibility spaces into concrete instantiated structures through guided self-organization, where Form exhibits both coherence and openness to further transformation}

proposals.name: The Paradox of Collective Individuation
proposals.formal: ∀consciousness c: (c.creative_potential maximized ⟺ c fully individuated as unique_I) ∧ (c.creative_potential maximized ⟺ c fully integrated within collective_WE) ∧ (unique_I ⊥ collective_WE). Maximum creative power requires both complete individual authenticity and complete collective integration, yet these appear mutually exclusive.
